Sentencas: We have studied magnetic correlations in several oxide materials that belong to colossal magnetoresistive, naturally occurring layered oxide showing low-dimensional magnetic ordering, solid oxide fuel cell interconnect materials, and magnetic nanoparticles using neutron diffraction and neutron depolarization techniques.
Titulo: Magnetic correlations in oxides: Neutron diffraction and neutron depolarization study

Sentencas: In this paper, an overview of some of these results is given.
Titulo: Magnetic correlations in oxides: Neutron diffraction and neutron depolarization study
